<br>
The only exception that I ever thought I might allow myself was if during an epic battle I was somehow involved in turning disaster into success. Not something simple like a raid to Splitpaw, but a dragon raid or plane raid. Then, if I managed to turn the tide of battle and save the day I migth take a name to honor the critter. Something like NaggySlayer. But it would only be related to a heroic dead and would not so much be a surname as a mini title.<br>
<br>
