<br>
although i do appreciate the beauty of some of the two-word names, i just think they're mostly silly and it gives you a three mile long nametag above your head.<br>
<br>
and yes, i did recommend that Form use one.  but that is really the quick and dirty way out.<br>
<br>
you could always pick something that sounds scottish.  almost every npc in halas is Mcsomething or other.  but that doesn't really lend itself to further description of your character, either.<br>
<br>
really it comes down to symbology.  what pictures do you want brought into the minds of people when they read your name?  it's difficult to pick one word that will bring to mind many things.<br>
<br>
